<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Any time a financial firm goes bankrupt, someo=
ne will trot out <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/3=
5377662.286337/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZ29vZHJlYWRzLmNvbS9xdW90ZXMvMTAyNTc5LWhvdy1k=
