olor: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; =
border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color:=
 #ccc;">wrote yesterday</a> about UBS Group AG=E2=80=99s plans to perhaps p=
ay its investment bankers bonuses if they refer business to its wealth mana=
gement business. I suggested that investment bankers would be =E2=80=9Chide=
ously embarrassed=E2=80=9D to pitch wealth management to their clients, but=
 that=E2=80=99s what the bosses want:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And so every big investment bank w=
ill from time to time announce an initiative that is like =E2=80=9Cwe=E2=80=
=99re going to tell our investment bankers that they should really mention =
our wealth management business to their corporate-executive clients,=E2=80=
=9D and it really does tell the investment bankers that, and the investment=
 bankers are like =E2=80=9Cyes we are team players and want to help our wea=
lth management colleagues bring in more revenue,=E2=80=9D but they shudder =
a little as they say it, and do they actually go out and pitch the wealth m=
anagement business? I don=E2=80=99t know, I=E2=80=99m not in the meetings.<=
/p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I got a few good reader emails. One reader wro=
te:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">A banker's reluctance to provide r=
eferrals to their wealth management colleagues may be caused by the increas=
ed relationship risk the referral brings,=C2=A0not necessarily their mercen=
ary nature.=C2=A0I can easily=C2=A0imagine the client conversation: =E2=80=
=9CNice job running the books on that bond issue, oh, and thanks for=C2=A0t=
he intro=C2=A0to your wealth management buddy. The money I gave him is trai=
ling my overall portfolio by 120 bps. I'll call you if I need your advice a=
gain.=E2=80=9D =E2=80=A6 Banking relationships are under enough competitive=
 pressure as is. Why introduce a new variable, over which you have no contr=
ol?</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And, sure, though if you are the chief executi=
ve officer of a big bank and you=E2=80=99re pushing for more cross-selling,=
 ideally=C2=A0<em>you=C2=A0</em>think that your wealth managers do a good j=
ob? Ideally you could=C2=A0<em>persuade=C2=A0</em>your investment bankers t=
hat their wealth management colleagues are actually competent? But, right, =
the investment bankers will be skeptical. Another reader wrote:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I am in a bunch of these meetings,=
 and I can affirm that they do go pitch the business, occasionally, gingerl=
y, usually in a walk-and-talk at a conference where the wealth manager was =
standing outside the door of the meeting room.</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Yes this is exactly how I pictured it. =E2=80=
=9CSo, it=E2=80=99s been great seeing you. Oh we also do wealth management.=
 Okay bye!=E2=80=9D</p>
